'''維拉斯奎斯宮'''（{{lang-es|Palacio de Velázquez}}）是一座位於[[西班牙|西班牙]]首都[[馬德里|馬德里]][[麗池公園|麗池公園]]的建築，又稱會展宮<ref name=" Stich 2001">{{cite book|last=Stich|first=Sidra|title=Spain: contemporary art + architecture handbook|url=https://archive.org/details/spaincontemporar00stic/page/98|accessdate=12 September 2012|year=2001|publisher=The University of Michigan|isbn=9780966771749|page=[https://archive.org/details/spaincontemporar00stic/page/98 98]}}</ref>。這座建築修建於1881年至1883年<ref name="Jorrín1992">{{cite book|last=Jorrín|first=Emilio|title=Efemerides Matritenses, 852-1992|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=KjAsAQAAMAAJ|accessdate=18 September 2012|year=1992|publisher=Avapiés|isbn=978-84-86280-59-8|page=68|language=es|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107183306/http://books.google.com/books?id=KjAsAQAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Gallagher2011">{{cite book|last=Gallagher|first=Mary-Ann|title=Frommer's Madrid Day By Day|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kNN7MtIMhkEC&pg=PA95|accessdate=18 September 2012|date=21 October 2011|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-1-119-97258-7|pages=95–}}</ref>，建築的內部裝飾可通過Google Street View觀看。

